MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 622

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE BARCELONITA SCHOOL OF FISHERIES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARANGAY BARCELONITA, MUNICIPALITY OF CABUSAO, PROVINCE OF CAMARINES SUR, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Barcelonita School of Fisheries, under the administration of the Secretary of Education, Culture and Sports, subject to private rights, if any there be, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Barangay Barcelonita, Municipality of Cabusao, Province of Camarines Sur, Island of Luzon, which is more particularly described as follows:

Plan Nr-05-000004 (Barcelonita Fisheries School)

A PARCEL OF LAND (Nr-05-000004), situated in Barangay Barcelonita, Municipality of Cabusao, Province of Camarines Sur, Island of Luzon. Bounded in the SE., along lines 8-1-2, by Public land; on the SW., along lines 2-3-4, by Protection Dike, Barcelonita-Cabusao (10.00 m. wide); on the NW., along line 4-5, by Outlet canal; along line 5-6, by Public Land; and on the NE., along lines 6-7-8, by San Miguel Bay. Beginning at a point marked “1” on the plan being S. 77 deg. 09’E., 883.76 m. from BBM No. 15, Pcadm-525-D, Cabusao Photo Cadastral Mapping.

147.02 m. to point 2;

332.92 m. to point 3;

237.43 m. to point 4;

137.49 m. to point 5;

50.00 m. to point 6;

244.99 m. to point 7;

297.56 m. to point 8;

40.00 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of ONE HUNDRED SIX THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED TWENTY EIGHT (106,228) SQUARE METERS. All corners referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. 15 x 40 cm. Bearings grid; date of survey on February 9, 1985 by Geodetic Engineer Isidro P. Palaypayon, and was approved on February 27, 1986.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 7th day of August , in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) CATALINO MACARAIG, JR. Executive Secretary

